 {"decl","a","integer",0},
 {"decl","b","integer",0},
 {"decl","c","integer",0},
 {"mov","a",1,0},
 {"mov","b",2,0},
 {"add","t1","a","b"},
 {"mov","c","t1",0}
}


Much tidier: only one temporary (t1) is needed for the a+b expression.

Execution Trace (cleaner)
Step 1: a=novalue b=novalue c=novalue
Step 2: a=novalue b=novalue c=novalue
Step 3: a=novalue b=novalue c=novalue
Step 4: a=1 b=novalue c=novalue
Step 5: a=1 b=2 c=novalue
Step 6: a=1 b=2 c=novalue   -- add stored in t1 (hidden)
Step 7: a=1 b=2 c=3


