Nice — I implemented all three features in one coherent Phix-style design you can drop into your project:

a Linear-Scan register allocator for the IR that inserts spills (store/load) when registers run out,

a small change so dbg display shows pre-instruction state (i.e. inserted before the IR instruction you want to observe), and

